  "body": "In `eth68`, in `NewPooledTransactionHashesMessage` there are sizes of transactions. Right now we are requesting all received (and not known) hashes in one `GetPooledTransactionsMessasge` and we will not receive them all if size of them exceeds max size of `PooledTransactionsMessage`. We should check sizes and request transactions in few messages, ensuring that every of them will not exceed max size",
